author: rwinston
msg: * Update UnixFTPEntryParser parser regex to enable parsing of timestamps with the day preceding the month. Currently the parser can be configured to use this style of timestamp, but the low-level matcher doesn't recognize it.
* Updare OS400FTPEntryParserTest: due to enhancements in UnixFTPEntryParser, some tests that were previously marked as bad now pass.
